Mombasa is a filthy drug hub and now partly a terror hotspot, and needs a big change to avoid losing tourists, Tourism CS Najib Balala has said. He said it has been difficult to sell the county and some of its specific tourist attractions sites, because of such &ldquo;an ugly face&rdquo;, Balala on Tuesday said.&ldquo;One cannot sleep with the door open or outside their homes, unlike years back.&rdquo;